DETAILS OF INFINIX SMART 7 4GB RAM 64GB ROM.Infinix is near to launch Smart 7 series of smartphones and it has been suggested that the devices may be launched in the upcoming months of this year, based on recent leaks.Then let's move on to the latest features of the Infinix Smart 7.Topping the list of features is a dual-lens camera setup, a 6.6-inch full-HD+ display, and a massive 6000 mAh battery with fast charging.In light of the fact that the smartphone might be launched with a massive 6000mAh battery pack, it is likely that users of this phone will be able to use it all day long on a single charge.Furthermore this Infinix Smart 7's a powerful Helio A22 SoC chipset with a couple of Octa-core CPUs.A dedicated memory card slot will enable users to expand the cell phone's memory up to 256GB in addition to the smartphone's 64GB of internal storage.

Up front we have the 5.2-inch display, above it are the earpiece, 5MP front camera, and sensors. Down below are three unlit capacitive navigation buttons for Options, Home, and Back.
On the left is the dual-SIM card tray for a nano and micro-sized SIMs. On the right are the volume keys and the power/lock button.
Up top are the headset jack and the dedicated microSD card slot. Down at the bottom are the microphone, microUSB port, and loudspeaker.
Flip it on its back and you will see the 8MP camera and LED flash, a couple of antenna bands, and the Vivo branding right in the middle.
On hand, the Y55 has a size that is neither too big nor too small, which makes it comfortable to hold even those with small hands. It has a chrome lining on the edges that adds extra grip while the back has a metallic matte finish that repels smudges and fingerprints well.

Product Name: Motorola Moto One 5G 4GB Ram 128GB Rom Single Sim
Product Specification:
Introducing the Motorola Moto One 5G – your gateway to the next era of connectivity and mobile technology. This smartphone packs 5G speed, stunning visuals, and impressive features into a sleek and affordable package.
Key Features:
1. 5G Connectivity: Step into the future with lightning-fast 5G connectivity, allowing you to stream, download, and game with minimal lag and incredible speed.
2. Immersive Display: Enjoy a 6.7-inch Max Vision Full HD+ display that delivers vibrant colors and sharp details, perfect for binge-watching, gaming, and browsing.
3. Dual Camera System: Capture incredible photos with the 48MP main camera and 8MP ultra-wide lens. The 16MP front camera ensures you take stunning selfies and engage in crystal-clear video calls.
4. Powerful Performance: Equipped with a Qualcomm Snapdragon 765 processor and 4GB of RAM, the Moto One 5G handles multitasking, gaming, and demanding apps with ease.
5. All-Day Battery: With a 5,000mAh battery, this phone keeps you powered up throughout your busy day, and when you need a quick recharge, TurboPower technology gets you back to full capacity swiftly.
6. Near-Stock Android: Experience the simplicity and efficiency of near-stock Android, with Motorola's thoughtful enhancements for an intuitive user interface.
7. Ample Storage: Store all your photos, apps, and files with 128GB of internal storage, expandable with a microSD card for additional space.
8. Water-Repellent Design: The Moto One 5G is designed to withstand accidental spills and splashes, offering added durability and peace of mind.
9. Fingerprint Sensor: Securely unlock your device and access your apps and data with the convenience of a rear-mounted fingerprint sensor.
10. Dedicated Google Assistant Button: Access Google Assistant with a single press, making it easier than ever to get answers, control your smart home devices, and more.
The Motorola Moto One 5G is your passport to the future, delivering high-speed connectivity, impressive camera capabilities, and reliable performance at an affordable price. Stay ahead of the curve with the Moto One 5G in your pocket.

It has a high pixel density of 400-500 PPI and a resolution of 1080p, making it perfect for watching videos and playing games. The phone is powered by an Octa-core processor and has 4GB of RAM memory, ensuring smooth and efficient performance. It has a large 5000 mAh battery with 18W fast charging, providing long-lasting battery life. The phone has three cameras, including a 17 MP front camera and a 50 MP back camera. It has a Nano sim type and two sim slots. The phone also has a headphone jack and supports fast charging. Overall, the VIVO y33s is a great choice for those looking for a high-performance mobile phone with a large screen, long battery life, and excellent camera capabilities.

Product Name: Tecno Spark 10 Pro 8+256GB || 50MP Rear Camera || 1 Year brand warranty || PTA Approved
Product Specification:
Considering all the latest features and specifications that it has, it might be considered to be the high-end variant of this series based on the leaks and news.
The Pro variant is expected to come with a larger display, a more powerful processor, more RAM, a bigger battery, and faster charging speeds.
It is also believed to come with a higher resolution camera, enabling users to take better pictures and videos. According to the rumours regarding Tecno's upcoming Spark 10 Pro, the device is expected to launch in the middle of March.
There is a 6.8 inch IPS LCD Capacitive Touchscreen display on this device that is capable of delivering the amazing resolution of 1080 x 2460 pixels, which is quite impressive.
Tecno Spark 10 possesses a single 32 MP selfie camera under the notch, which can be used to record and capture high-definition videos and images.
An array of dual camera can be found on the back of the phone.
According to the press release, the main sensor will be 50 MP and the others have not yet been confirmed.
With the powerful MediaTek Helio G88 SoC chipset and the octa-core 2.0 GHz CPU, the Tecno Spark's 10 Pro is equipped with all the power you need to run the smartphone smoothly.
Following that, it is expected to be equipped with 8GB of RAM as well as 128GB of internal storage.
A dedicated memory card slot will then be present on the Spark 10 Pro for the purpose of expanding the memory. Currently, there is no official date that has been set for the launch of the phone.
On the new 10 Pro, you will find a bigger battery cell that will allow you to run it all day on one charge; it has a capacity of 5000 mAh.
Additionally, it has the capability of supporting fast charging as well.
